  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Dialog: Rack-Pinion / Ball-screw</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">Rack-Pinion / Ball-Screw</para>
    <para styleclass="SeeAlso">See: <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Mechanism-Rack-Pinion">Add Rack-Pinion</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Use the <text styleclass="Element">Rack-Pinion</text>&#32;<text styleclass="Element">dialog-box</text> to edit parameters for a <text styleclass="Element">Rack-Pinion</text><text styleclass="VariableName-indent">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">You can use the <text styleclass="Element">Rack-Pinion dialog-box</text> to convert the <text styleclass="Element">Rack-Pinion</text> to a <text styleclass="Element">Ball-Screw</text>.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">Open Rack-Pinion dialog-box</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Standard" rowcount="1" colcount="2" style="width:auto; head-row-background-color:#ffffff; alt-row-background-color:none;">
      <thead style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:240px; border-right:none;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MD-GA-EditRackPinion.png" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td style="border-left:none;">
          <para styleclass="Body Text">Edit the<text styleclass="Element"> Rack-Pinion</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="PopupTable2" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="border-top:none; border-right:none; border-bottom:none;">
                <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="B Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="Body Text">Double-click a </text><text styleclass="Element">Rack-Pinion </text><text styleclass="Body Text">in the </text><text styleclass="Interface">graphic-area</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> or </text><text styleclass="Interface">Assembly-Tree</text><text styleclass="Body Text">.</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="VariableName-IT">- or -</para>
                <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="B Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="SeeAlso">See </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-How-to-Open-a-Dialog-Box" styleclass="SeeAlso">How to Open a Dialog-Box</link><text styleclass="VariableName"> &#160;</text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Normal">The </text><text styleclass="Element">Rack-Pinion dialog-box</text><text styleclass="Normal"> is now open.</text></para>
        </td>
      </thead>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">Rack-Pinion / Ball-Screw dialog-box</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Standard" rowcount="1" colcount="2" style="width:auto;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:235px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><image src="MD-DIALOG-RACKPINION.ipp" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">There are three tabs in the <text styleclass="Element">Rack-Pinion dialog-box</text>. Each tab has one separator.</para>
          <para styleclass="Heading4 HowTo Toggle_atoc_">General tab</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets"><text styleclass="Separator-Header">Rack and Pinion Parameters</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Heading4 HowTo Toggle_atoc_">Gear Tooth tab</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets"><text styleclass="Separator-Header">Rack and Pinion Tooth Parameters</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Heading4 HowTo Toggle_atoc_">Ball-Screw tab</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets"><text styleclass="Separator-Header">Ball-Screw Parameters</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 HowTo_atoc_">General tab :</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><anchor id="RackPinionParameters" styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_"><keywords><keyword>Rack and Pinion Gear Parameters</keyword></keywords></anchor><image src="btn_addkeyword.bmp" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Separator-Header" figurelistinclude="0"></image><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" src-collapsed="btn_addkeyword.bmp" src-expanded="btn_delkeyword.bmp" src-print="none" styleclass="Separator-Header"><caption><![CDATA[ Rack and Pinion Parameters ]]></caption></toggle></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Standard" rowcount="1" colcount="2" style="width:auto;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:246px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MD-Dialog-RackPinion-General.png" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Parameter-Header">Shift the Rack by:</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text style="font-style:normal;">Move</text> the <text styleclass="Element">rack</text> along its pitch-line by # number-of-teeth.</para>
          <para styleclass="Parameter-Header">Number-of-Teeth, Rack:</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The <text styleclass="Parameter">number-of-teeth</text> on the <text styleclass="Element">Rack</text>. </para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Edit the <text styleclass="Parameter">Number-of-Teeth</text> on the <text styleclass="Element">Rack</text> so that it stays in mesh with the <text styleclass="Element">Pinion</text> for a machine-cycle</para>
          <para styleclass="Parameter-Header"># Number-of-Teeth, Pinion:</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The number-of-teeth on the <text styleclass="Element">Pinion.</text>&#32;</para>
          <para styleclass="Parameter-Header">Align Mesh:</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">When <text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">you add two(2) </text><text styleclass="Element">Racks</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> to one(1) </text><text styleclass="Element">Pinion</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">, you will usually see two(2) </text><text styleclass="Element">Pinions</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> on the same axis. If you want</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> to see one(1) </text><text styleclass="Element">Pinion</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">, click one of these options:</text></para>
          <list id="2" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#164;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:Wingdings; font-size:10pt; color:#333399;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Parameter">Shift Rack</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Parameter">Shift Pinion</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Parameter">Do not Shift</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Parameter-Header">Select Rack Side:</para>
          <list id="3" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#164;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; font-family:Wingdings; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px;"><text styleclass="Parameter">Right </text><text styleclass="Body Text">(default) </text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">When the <text styleclass="Element">Pinion</text> (Ball-Screw) rotates <text styleclass="VariableName">Counter-Clockwise</text>, the <text styleclass="Element">Rack</text> (Nut) move in the <text styleclass="VariableName">Positive-Direction</text> of the <text styleclass="Element">Slide-Joint</text>&#32;</para>
          <list id="3" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#164;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; font-family:Wingdings; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px;"><text styleclass="Parameter">Left </text>&#32;</li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">When the <text styleclass="Element">Pinion</text> (Ball-Screw) rotates <text styleclass="VariableName">Clockwise</text>, the <text styleclass="Element">Rack </text>(Nut) move in the <text styleclass="VariableName">Negative-Direction</text> of the <text styleclass="Element">Slide-Joint</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 HowTo_atoc_">Gear Tooth tab :</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><anchor id="RackPinion-Gear-Tooth-tab" styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_"><keywords><keyword>Rack-Pinion dialog<keyword>Gear Tooth tab</keyword></keyword></keywords></anchor><image src="btn_addkeyword.bmp" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Separator-Header" figurelistinclude="0"></image><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" src-collapsed="btn_addkeyword.bmp" src-expanded="btn_delkeyword.bmp" src-print="none" styleclass="Separator-Header"><caption><![CDATA[ Rack and Pinion Tooth Parameters ]]></caption></toggle></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Standard" rowcount="8" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td rowspan="8" style="width:245px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:right;"><image src="MD-Dialog-RackPinion-GearTeeth.png" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td style="border-bottom:none;">
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Gear-Module" styleclass="Parameter-Header">Module</link><text styleclass="Parameter">&#32;</text><text style="font-weight:bold;">=</text> P.C.D. ÷ <text styleclass="Parameter">Number-of-Teeth</text> on <text styleclass="Element">Pinion</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="background-color:#f0f0f0; border-top:none; border-bottom:none;">
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo2"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Rack/Pinion Ratio</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> (</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="font-size:10pt; vertical-align:baseline;">degrees</text><text styleclass="Body Text">),</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> per Rack Displacement</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> (</text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-size:10pt; vertical-align:baseline;">mm</text><text styleclass="Body Text">)</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="background-color:#f0f0f0; border-top:none; border-bottom:none;">
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Pitch Circle Diameter </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">(P.C.D.) (</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="font-size:10pt; vertical-align:baseline;">mm</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">) (Read-Only)</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The diameter of the Pitch Circle of the Pinion</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text">P.C.D. (</text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-size:10pt; vertical-align:baseline;">mm</text><text styleclass="Body Text">) = &#160;Number-of-Teeth × Module</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="border-top:none; border-bottom:none;">
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Gear-Pressure-Angle" styleclass="Parameter-Header">Pressure Angle</link><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">:</text> (Default <text style="font-weight:bold;">=</text> 20º). </para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The Pressure Angle is usually 20º. Other standard Pressure-Angles are: <text style="font-weight:normal;">14º</text>, 17.5º (weaker, quieter), <text style="font-weight:normal;">22.5º and 25º</text> (stronger, noisier).</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="border-top:none; border-bottom:none;">
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Addendum:</text> (Usually <text style="font-weight:bold;">=</text> Module). </para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The radial height of the gear tooth from the pitch circle to the tip of the tooth.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="border-top:none; border-bottom:none;">
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Dedendum:</text> (Usually = Module * 1.25 (Module&gt;1)). </para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The radial depth of the gear tooth below the Pitch Circle to the root of the tooth. It is larger than the Addendum so there is clearance. Then the tip of the tooth is clear of the root of the </para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="border-top:none; border-bottom:none;">
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Root Radius:</text> (Usually = &#160;0.3 * Module)</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The small fillet between the Flank and the Root of the Gear Tooth.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="border-top:none;">
          <para styleclass="Parameter-Header">Points per Tooth Flank:</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The number of &apos;facets&apos; along the gear tooth flank. &apos;: &#160;6 is OK, 8 is Good. </para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 HowTo_atoc_">Ball-Screw tab :</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><anchor id="Rack-Pinion-BallScrew-tab" styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_"><keywords><keyword>Rack-Pinion dialog<keyword>Ball-Screw parameters</keyword></keyword></keywords></anchor><image src="btn_addkeyword.bmp" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Separator-Header" figurelistinclude="0"></image><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" src-collapsed="btn_addkeyword.bmp" src-expanded="btn_delkeyword.bmp" src-print="none" styleclass="Separator-Header"><caption><![CDATA[ Ball Screws Parameters ]]></caption></toggle></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Standard" rowcount="1" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:242px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:right;"><image src="MD-Dialog-RackPinion-BallScrewParams.png" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Parameter-Header">Select Type</para>
          <list id="4" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#162;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="2" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:Wingdings; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Parameter">Rack and Pinion</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> (default) </text></li>
          </list>
          <list id="5" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#164;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:Wingdings; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Parameter">Ball-Screw</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text">The symbol in the </text><text styleclass="Interface">graphic-area</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> of a </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Ball-Screw</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> is a </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Helix/Screw</text><text styleclass="Body Text">, starting at the </text><text styleclass="Interface">start-Point</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> of the </text><text styleclass="Interface">sliding-Part</text><text styleclass="Body Text">. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <list id="6" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Ball-Screw Lead</text> (<text style="font-size:10pt; vertical-align:baseline;">mm</text>) - distance the <text styleclass="Interface">Sliding-Part</text> moves after one(1) rotation of the <text styleclass="Interface">Rotating-Part.</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Ball-Screw Diameter</text> (<text style="font-size:10pt; vertical-align:baseline;">mm</text>) - diameter of the <text styleclass="Interface">Ball-Screw</text> symbol in the <text styleclass="Interface">graphic-area</text>.</li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Notes">Notes:</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The length of the <text styleclass="Element">Ball-Screw</text> Length is the length of the Line in the <text styleclass="Interface">sliding-Part</text> - see <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Mechanism-Rack-Pinion">Add Rack-Pinion</link>.</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The <text styleclass="VariableName">Nut</text> (<text styleclass="Interface">Sliding-Part</text>) of the <text styleclass="Element">Ball-Screw</text> moves in a <text styleclass="VariableName">Positive-Direction</text> of the <text styleclass="Element">Slide-Joint</text> when the <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-RackPinion" anchor="RackPinionParameters" styleclass="Parameter">Rack-Side</link> is set to <text styleclass="Parameter">Right </text><text styleclass="Body Text">- </text><text styleclass="SeeAlso">see </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-RackPinion" anchor="RackPinionParameters" styleclass="SeeAlso">General tab</link></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="page-break-before:always;"></para>
